    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 10/5/16 at 2:26 pm CT</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.10-ReturnRepairDevices\">Return Repair Devices</h3><p>The recent 1.8.9 update introduced an optimization for loading customer devices on a ticket, but this caused a regression\u00a0for new return repair tickets where the\u00a0originally repaired device would not always be\u00a0pre-selected on the new return repair ticket. This issue has been resolved.</p>",
